net.ssehub.comani.analysis.variabilitychange.diff

Class DiffAnalyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.ssehub.comani.analysis.variabilitychange.diff.DiffAnalyzer

  • public class DiffAnalyzer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements a general diff analyzer.

    This class is used to provide the numbers of changed lines in different file types of a specific commit. In turn, this class uses the different file diff classes depending on the type of file changed by the given commit.
    Author:
    Christian Kroeher
